{"tid":1497221,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日波羅的海人鏈一定要出嚟。 唔夠人下場會好可憐，幫手宣傳出去。","createTime":"2019-08-23T01:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:43:40.000Z","uid":43785,"like":212,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"a1661abbd0b20c78251abcafa1d720f05a7c333d","tid":1497221,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"今日波羅的海人鏈一定要出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n事緣係咁既， 啱啱返到公司， 聽到啲同事喺度討論， 發現原來好多人都唔睇好呢一件事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「 我覺得今晚一定唔夠人囉。」<br />\n「今日收咗工會去地鐵站集合都係戇鳩。」<br />\n「難得星期五，一定會去食下嘢， 約阿女仔，扑下嘢。」<br />\n「我上去揼轉骨好撚過啦」<br />\n「點會同你夜媽媽出嚟企喺馬路邊食塵。」<br />\n「地鐵站太散， 班曱甴連到三個站都當你贏」<br />\n<br />\n面對咁撚多藍絲帶同事， 有時真係覺得自己返工係去咗平行時空。<br />\n各位今日一定要出嚟，唔好俾班藍屍帶睇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞唔成一定有排笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國睇完都覺得香港人唔齊心，以後搞乜都搞唔成。<br />\n唔該各位用盡所有渠道宣傳<br />\n威迫利誘你哋嘅兄弟家人出嚟築成人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n拖手其實係一樣好閒嘅事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好介意拖手， 唔會生bb，唔會有任何野。<br />\n愛自己，愛香港，拖一次。"},{"pid":"f707c1ee5f5ba6ee400ee8a68f4abed48280112b","tid":1497221,"uid":173058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:13:00.000Z","msg":"今晚會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d88c8992212e2383ecd7538f5e6f207c053e776","tid":1497221,"uid":43785,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m99CSsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm99CSsj.jpg&h=f279a13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不要忘記"},{"pid":"60c226a1cad0c59583df5375edcac91447e720d7","tid":1497221,"uid":174882,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUR2i7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUR2i7p.png&h=6995595d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c406b226dbb2364fba687a92791799e4dc1ec8a9","tid":1497221,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTtHi7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTtHi7v.jpg&h=9eeefdad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8uCSsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8uCSsx.jpg&h=ef83e11c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zcTPJzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzcTPJzd.jpg&h=21a8a7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHDoN0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHDoN0X.jpg&h=51dff8af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33c10e76bb55f08e5a2936e47951df9981ceec35","tid":1497221,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"專登入黎睇你比人話「同事」係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292c40b809dcc636fffd3f07e5023d37a648c0d5","tid":1497221,"uid":102491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將所有核彈列明黎推post<br />\n歡迎增加任用<br />\n<br />\n置頂 曱甴論+動用私刑+日日講大話！<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 無啦啦拘捕個女人<br />\n5. 室內開槍<br />\n6. 過份使用武力+催淚彈<br />\n7. 冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警黑勾結<br />\n10. 無差別濫捕<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話<br />\n12. 誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n13. 拆證物<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引<br />\n15. 葉虎事件<br />\n16. 因應政見決定做野同起訴速度<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人 清算黑警<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"bfa48ee2ba28400ecbae4fa852cf4a3436ab14a3","tid":1497221,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"[8.23香港之路]邊個站最多學生妹 應該去邊個站好?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496995</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a633730fb